$ SQL*Plus: SET ARRAYSIZE
@ set arraysize

The maximum value for `arraysize` is 5000.

sa:

  The default value of `arraysize` is changed when using SQL*Plus's `-fast` → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus#sql-plus-start-options[command line option].

  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus/set[`set`]

  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus
